Uintah-specific Kokkos documentation can be found at http://uintah-build.sci.utah.edu/trac/wiki/Kokkos.

Kokkos installation instructions can be found in src/build_scripts/build_kokkos.

An example of Kokkos usage within Uintah can be found in src/CCA/Components/Examples/Poisson1.cc.

A collection of Kokkos tutorials can be found at https://github.com/kokkos/kokkos-tutorials.

The Kokkos programming guide can be found in KOKKOS_PATH/doc/Kokkos_PG.pdf.